<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Bienvenue à Badarel · Auvergne</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700&family=Lato:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
  body { background:#f7f3ec; font-family:'Lato',sans-serif; font-weight:300; color:#2e2018; min-height:100vh; display:flex; flex-direction:column; }

  .hero {
    position:relative; height:380px; overflow:hidden;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  }
  .hero img {
    position:absolute; inset:0; width:100%; height:100%;
    object-fit:cover; object-position:center 55%;
  }
  .hero::after {
    content:''; position:absolute; inset:0;
    background:linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,.15), rgba(0,0,0,.65));
  }
  .hero-text {
    position:relative; z-index:2; text-align:center; color:white; padding:24px;
  }
  .hero-badge {
    display:inline-block; background:rgba(255,255,255,.18);
    border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.4); font-size:11px;
    letter-spacing:3px; text-transform:uppercase; padding:5px 16px;
    border-radius:20px; margin-bottom:14px;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;
    font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3.2rem); font-weight:700; line-height:1.2;
    margin-bottom:10px;
  }
  .hero h1 em { font-style:italic; color:#b8dfc6; }
  .hero p { font-size:1rem; opacity:.88; }

  main {
    max-width:700px; margin:0 auto; padding:52px 22px 60px;
    flex:1; width:100%;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; font-size:1.4rem;
    color:#3a6b4d; text-align:center; margin-bottom:32px;
    font-weight:400; font-style:italic;
  }

  .cards { display:grid; gap:18px; }

  .card {
    background:white; border-radius:16px;
    box-shadow:0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
    text-decoration:none; color:inherit;
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:20px;
    padding:22px 24px;
    transition:transform .2s, box-shadow .2s;
    border-left:5px solid #3a6b4d;
  }
  .card:hover {
    transform:translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow:0 8px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.13);
  }
  .card.orange { border-left-color:#bf6e3a; }
  .card.blue   { border-left-color:#4a7fa5; }

  .card-ico {
    font-size:2.4rem; flex-shrink:0; line-height:1;
  }
  .card-title {
    font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;
    font-size:1.15rem; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:4px;
    color:#2e2018;
  }
  .card-desc { font-size:.87rem; color:#777; line-height:1.55; }
  .card-arrow {
    margin-left:auto; font-size:1.3rem; color:#3a6b4d;
    flex-shrink:0; opacity:.6;
  }
  .card.orange .card-arrow { color:#bf6e3a; }
  .card.blue   .card-arrow { color:#4a7fa5; }

  footer {
    background:#2e2018; color:rgba(255,255,255,.55);
    text-align:center; padding:24px; font-size:.82rem;
  }
  footer strong { color:white; }

  @media(max-width:500px){
    .hero { height:280px; }
    .card { padding:18px; gap:14px; }
    .card-ico { font-size:2rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hero">
  <img src="hero_terrasse.jpg" alt="Terrasse teck – Badarel, Bansat">
  <div class="hero-text">
    <div class="hero-badge">🌿 Hameau de Badarel · Bansat</div>
    <h1>Bienvenue dans<br>ma <em>maison</em> !</h1>
    <p>12 lieu-dit Badarel · 63570 Bansat · Auvergne</p>
  </div>
</div>

<main>
  <h2>Choisissez votre document</h2>

  <div class="cards">

    <a class="card" href="livret_accueil_badarel.html">
      <span class="card-ico">🏠</span>
      <div>
        <div class="card-title">Livret d'accueil</div>
        <div class="card-desc">WiFi, équipements, poêle à bois, éco-gestes, départ… Tout ce qu'il faut savoir pour votre séjour à Badarel.</div>
      </div>
      <span class="card-arrow">→</span>
    </a>

    <a class="card orange" href="guide_activites_badarel.html">
      <span class="card-ico">🥾</span>
      <div>
        <div class="card-title">Guide des activités</div>
        <div class="card-desc">Randonnées, plan d'eau, parc animalier, villages, marchés, bonnes tables, festivités… Le meilleur de la région.</div>
      </div>
      <span class="card-arrow">→</span>
    </a>

    <a class="card blue" href="livret_accessible_badarel.html">
      <span class="card-ico">👁</span>
      <div>
        <div class="card-title">Livret accessible</div>
        <div class="card-desc">Version grande police et fort contraste — conçue pour les personnes malvoyantes ou dyslexiques.</div>
      </div>
      <span class="card-arrow">→</span>
    </a>

  </div>
</main>

<footer>
  <strong>Havre de paix écorénovée · Hameau de Badarel · 63570 Bansat · Auvergne</strong><br>
  Sidonie · 06 64 51 32 45 · Votre voisine directe 🌿
</footer>

</body>
</html>
